title: Synthwave Cinematic Electronic SciFi Music
description: This music pack contains 18 tracks of Cinematic Electronic SciFi Music in a true Synthwave style. These songs are a mix of energy, action, atmosphere and tension, making them PERFECT for action RPGs, sci-fi games, tactical shooters and more.
longDescription:
This music pack contains 11 tracks, 1 main theme, 6 action tracks and 4 exploration tracks. Additionally, I added alternative exploratory versions of the main theme and the 6 action tracks, giving a total of 18 tracks of Cinematic Electronic SciFi Music in a true Synthwave style. These songs are a mix of energy, action, atmosphere and tension, making them perfect for action RPGs, sci-fi games, tactical shooters and more.


Tracklist:

  1. Chronicles of the Cyber Hero [Loop]
  2. Cybernetic Combat [Loop]
  3. Nuclear Nexus [Loop]
  4. Digital Destruction [Loop]
  5. Adrenaline Assault [Loop]
  6. Cybernetic Clash – Drill Protocol [Loop]
  7. Heroic Ascendance – Final Clash [Loop]
  8. Urban Odyssey [Loop]
  9. Techscape Traverse [Loop]
  10. Neon Horizons [Loop]
  11. Circuit Serenade [Loop]


Alternative Versión Exploration:

  1. Cybernetic Combat [Loop]
  2. Nuclear Nexus [Loop]
  3. Digital Destruction [Loop]
  4. Adrenaline Assault [Loop]
  5. Cybernetic Clash – Drill Protocol [Loop]
  6. Chronicles of the Cyber Hero [Loop]
  7. Heroic Ascendance Final Clash [Loop]


I hope these clues serve you well for your action RPGs, sci-fi games or tactical shooters! You don’t need to credit me or purchase a license to use them in your commercial game, but I’d love to know when and how you use this music so I can share your game with my audience.


Best,

Tito Lopez.


https://youtu.be/fn6JMIH8mMk


https://soundcloud.com/titolopez-music/sets/synthwave-cinematic-electronic-scifi-music
